****DROPDOWNS******
-Hovver effects on an elements displays a "dropdown" list of elements
-In reality, elements are merely hidden until the hover effect changes display : none to display:block
header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-contnet: space-between;
}

 .dropdown {
     width: 200px
     font-size: 30px
 }

 ul {
     display: none;
     position: absolute;
     top: 30px
 }

 .dropdown:hover ul {
    display: block
 }

 li:hover {
     background-color: gray;
     cursor: pointer;
 }


 